'''Stoneshoulder''' may refer to:
* [[Stoneshoulder]], a dwarven clan of [[the North]];
* [[Iirikos Stoneshoulder]], a famed [[dwarf]] architect and artisan of [[Ammarindar]];
* [[Bettargh Stoneshoulder]], a dwarf high priest of [[Dugmaren Brightmantle]] in [[Iltkazar]];
* [[Dunnabar Stoneshoulder]], a dwarf high priest of [[Gorm Gulthyn]] in Iltkazar;
* [[Hall of Stoneshoulder]], a [[guild]] hall in Iltkazar;
* [[Untieus Boldenbar]], a dwarf of [[Sarbreen]] nicknamed "Stoneshoulders";
* [[Stoneshoulder (noble family)]], a noble family of [[Procampur]] in [[the Vast]];
* [[Elephon Stoneshoulder]], a [[horse]] breeder of the Procampan Stoneshoulders; or
* [[Stoneshoulder Creek]], a creek in [[the Ride]] and [[Moonsea North]].
